data.description: Welcome to 183 Goldshore Way - an open concept 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom ranch that is waiting for you to call it home. Walking distance to Statham Elementary, shops, and dining. The bright and sunny interior has been immaculately upgraded with a whole home HVAC air purification system, premium lighting, plumbing fixtures, flooring, and more. A spacious family room with vaulted ceiling and cozy fireplace invites you in to relax and enjoy quality time with family and friends. The chef's kitchen features an oversized (87x38) granite island with breakfast bar, ample cabinetry, pantry, and stainless steel appliances. Easy access to the dining room. flex space, and outdoor oasis make this home perfect for entertaining. The primary suite boasts a tray ceiling, wifi controlled ceiling fan, and spa-like en-suite bath with large walk-in closet, granite top double vanity, soaking tub, and shower with custom shower door. 3 additional guest rooms with a shared full bathroom gives you room to grow! The landscaped property is a sanctuary of relaxation - privacy fenced with a lighted inflatable hot tub awaits under a shaded pergola. You can also cool off in the 15 ft x 48 inch round heated above ground pool with a new sand filter pump. Need room to store items? Look no further than the stick built 10x15 workshop with built in shelving and ramp for ease of use. Schedule your showing today!
